reviews.reviewText: 3 things:1. Okay quality2. Bang for your buck3. Amazing cleaning/prep suppliesTo start off, the quality was not that good for the screen protectors. reviews.reviewText: These have been fantastic for my daughter's phone. They protected the screen from multiple drops! Very pleased.

Even beginners can successfully put a screen protector with their kit and instructions. No problem with screen responding with this protector on. Will definitely recommend to others and repurchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: Dependable Protection for My iPhone 12 Mini
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the JETech Screen Protector for iPhone 12 Mini, and once again, this brand has proven to be my go-to choice for reliable screen protection. The 3-pack of tempered glass films provides excellent coverage for my device, and I couldn't be happier with the overall performance.Installation was a breeze, thanks to the clear instructions and the inclusion of all the necessary tools in the package. No annoying bubbles or misalignments. Within minutes, my iPhone 12 Mini's screen was safeguarded against scratches, smudges, and everyday wear and tear.One of the standout features of the JETech Screen Protector is its durability. The tempered glass feels sturdy and robust, providing a strong defence against accidental drops and impacts. The clarity of the screen remains unaffected, ensuring that the vibrant display of my iPhone 12 Mini shines through without any compromise in visibility.The touch sensitivity of the screen is as responsive as ever, with no noticeable lag or interference from the protector.What sets JETech apart for me is the consistency in quality across their products. Having used their screen protectors for previous devices, I can confidently say that they have maintained their high standards. This reliability is a significant factor in why I keep coming back to this brand for all my screen protector needs.JETech Screen Protector for iPhone 12 Mini is a top-notch choice for anyone seeking dependable and durable screen protection. With easy installation, robust construction, and a brand that consistently delivers on its promises, I have once again found peace of mind in knowing that my device is well-protected.
